###
GET http://localhost:8082/api/trading/positions?
    instId=BTC-USDT

###
GET http://localhost:8082/api/trading/positions/history?
    instId=BTC-USDT&
    before=1740960000000

### Создание шорт лимитного ордера
POST http://localhost:8082/api/trading/futures/limit/short
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instrument": "BTC-USDT",
  "limitPrice": 73840,
  "positionSizeUsdt": 30,
  "stopLossPercent": 1,
  "takeProfitPercent": 3
}

